      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate your<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Dissolve your<strong> pho broth paste</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]<strong> </span>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>pho stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1680014116218-x200.jpg",
