            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basa fillets</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>turmeric cornflour</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa</strong> to the <strong>turmeric</strong> <strong>cornflour</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully coated, then set aside for later – these are your <strong>coated basa</strong> <strong>pieces</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1680014121770-x200.jpg",
