            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> grated ginger</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once softened, add your <strong>ground coriander</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant – this is your <strong>ginger & shallot mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1680014124476-x200.jpg",
