        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wipe the reserved pan clean and return it to a medium-high heat with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa pieces </strong>and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until golden and crisp – this is your <strong>crispy turmeric basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
